  "body": "When reading https://docs.openzeppelin.com/contracts/5.x/utilities#payment there is a link to a `PaymentSplitter` contract that no longer exists. Moreover, the rationale for removing this contract or the `PullPayment` contract are not documented anywhere.\r\n\r\n**üíª Environment**\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\n\r\nThe rationale for these code removals is not properly documented in the changelog, and I wasn't able to find the motivation for removing this code anywhere else, nor a valid alternative approach.\r\n\r\n**üî¢ Code to reproduce bug**\r\n",
